    "longBusinessSummary": "Water Supply Sewerage Construction and Investment Joint Stock Company operates as a general contractor for construction and installation of water supply and drainage works, wastewater treatment, and technical infrastructure projects in Vietnam. The company provides clean water for residents and industrial parks; invests in building clean water plants; trades in water industry equipment and materials, and construction materials; funds for building of houses, commercial areas, and offices for rent; invests in wind power and solar power production projects; consults and appraises construction investment projects; prepares and verifies total and project budgets; designs review and total estimates; designs and supervises construction of water supply and drainage works, urban technical infrastructure, and civil and industrial works. It also engages in the construction and installation of civil - industrial and traffic works; waterways, ports, river, and irrigation works; and environmental sanitation works and solar battery systems, as well as real estate business; building and renting of banks, supermarkets, hospitals, and shopping centers; and clean water production business. The company was founded in 1975 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. Water Supply Sewerage Construction and Investment Joint Stock Company is a subsidiary of Vietnam Water and Environment Investment Corporation - JSC.",
